Package org.colomoto.biolqm.io.petrinet Description

Petri net support. This format adds export filter to some Petri net formats. Logical models are first transformed into Petri net using the method described in Chaouiya2007 (doi: 10.1093/bib/bbm029). Some popular formats are supported: PNT (INA), APNN, and PNML
